Competition from other types of pumps: There is increasing competition from other types of pumps, such as API pumps and magnetically coupled pumps. This is a major restraint of the market.
Fluctuations in raw material prices: The prices of raw materials, such as steel and copper, are volatile. This volatility can affect the cost of ANSI pumps and their demand.




